The upper of the Jordan 1 Low Spades utilizes embossed red paisley designs atop of black leather. A gold Swoosh adds further bright, luxe detail to the sneaker with a spades decal stitched on the tongue tag. Lastly, a gold �Q� and �K� is embroidered closer to the toe of the sneaker for Queen and King of a card deck.
